[30;1m270 | [0m[35mWe use Python's built-in :mod:`unittest` module to structure our tests,[0m
[30;1m271 | [0m[35mwhich are placed in the :file:`neo/test` directory.[0m
[30;1m272 | [0m[35mRelated tests are grouped into classes, and each individual test is a method of that class,[0m
[30;1m273 | [0m[35mso take a look at the existing tests before deciding whether to add a new method,[0m
[30;1m274 | [0m[35ma new class or a new file.[0m
[30;1m275 | [0m[35m[0m

[30;1m61 | [0m[35m    AxoGraph file format, even time was stored as a 1-dimensional array. In[0m
[30;1m62 | [0m[35m    newer versions, time is stored as a special type of "column" that is really[0m
[30;1m63 | [0m[35m    just a starting time and a sampling period.[0m
[30;1m64 | [0m[35m[0m
